# Omninuera — AI Intern Offer Letter (Draft)  
Redlined / Annotated Version — Suggested edits are shown inline. HR: DO NOT ISSUE this version directly — use to update the official offer.

> Notes on markup conventions used here:
> - ~~struck text~~ = suggested deletion
> - **[INSERT: ...]** = suggested insertion (copy-paste text below where indicated)
> - {COMMENT: ...} = advisor commentary for HR/legal
> - Text shown with no markup is original.

